title: $:/xp/details-button/readme

A button ({{$:/core/images/details}}) for the Editor toolbar adds a HTML5 `<details>` element. The `<details>` tag specifies additional details that the user can open and close on demand. 

Assigned shortcut: {{$:/config/shortcuts/details}}

